Java Week 9 Question 5 code:
class Point {
    private double x;
    private double y;

    public Point(double x, double y) {
        this.x = x;
        this.y = y;
    }

    public double distance(Point p2) {
        double disto;
        disto = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(this.x - p2.x, 2) + Math.pow(this.y - p2.y, 2));
        return disto;
    }
}

